(2329, 254, '_section_4_content_0_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(2330, 254, 'section_4_content_0_text', 'Our extensive knowledge and experience in our industry ensures that we provide the most up to date, fair and honest quotes. We offer cost saving where we can and provide recommendations to get the most out of pre-designed projects. Our established relationships with our subtrades, provide our customers with an impressive, well rounded Mechanical team.'),
(2331, 254, '_section_4_content_0_text', 'field_5c48efe172bf1'),
(2332, 254, 'section_4_content_1_image', '233'),
(2333, 254, '_section_4_content_1_image', 'field_5c48f4fdd276b'),
(2334, 254, 'section_4_content_1_headline', 'Design Build'),
(2335, 254, '_section_4_content_1_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(2336, 254, 'section_4_content_1_text', 'World Class Contracting takes great pride in being a part of the design of a project. Including us in the design process helps to eliminate many design conflicts that can occur structurally, architecturally and between the other trades. This proactive approach in turn helps to save the project time and money early on.'),
(2337, 254, '_section_4_content_1_text', 'field_5c48efe172bf1'),
(2338, 254, 'section_4_content_2_image', '233'),
(2339, 254, '_section_4_content_2_image', 'field_5c48f4fdd276b'),
(2340, 254, 'section_4_content_2_headline', 'IPD'),
(2341, 254, '_section_4_content_2_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(2342, 254, 'section_4_content_2_text', 'World Class Contracting has become well versed in the relatively new IPD philosophy and process. Similar to a Design Build approach; working as a team from the beginning of the IPD project creates a well thought out plan of what the owner envisions, and has proven to be a very effective way to deliver an exceptional final project.'),
(2343, 254, '_section_4_content_2_text', 'field_5c48efe172bf1'),
(2344, 254, 'section_4_content_3_image', '233'),
