(2693, 267, 'section_2_text', 'World Class Contracting is looking for people who believe in accountability & integrity; who have a commitment to lifelong learning and enjoy taking on new opportunities and responsibilities and intend to grow their career. We take great pride in the team of highly skilled people we have built through these efforts.'),
