(3078, 277, 'section_5_text', 'The World Class Contracting Ltd. (WCC) name was chosen after President, Jordan Hindbo, represented Canada in the 1999 World Skills Competition setting out with a vision to create an organization that performs “World Class” craftsmanship'),
