(3905, 299, '_section_2_headline', 'field_5c4a47eb4bbe3'),
(3906, 299, 'section_2_text', 'World Class Contracting offers experience, innovative ideas and the desire and dedication to provide an exceptional building experience to our customers, all backed by a solid team of highly skilled tradespeople. WCC is committed to seeking innovative solutions, exceeding expectations with quality, timely construction, and safety excellence.\r\n\r\nOur Expertise ranges from designing, installing and retrofitting mechanical systems in Commercial, Greenhouse Growing Facilities, Municipal, Institutional, Education, Sports &amp; Leisure, Multi-family Residential, Estates, and Healthcare facilities. We have the capability of providing and designing 3D drawings which assist in visual planning and enables prefabrication welding for mechanical rooms, which is an advantage to construction schedules.'),
(3907, 299, '_section_2_text', 'field_5c4a47fc4bbe4'),
(3908, 299, 'section_3_content_0_headline', 'Our Commitment'),
(3909, 299, '_section_3_content_0_headline', 'field_5c4a484e4bbe7'),
(3910, 299, 'section_3_content_0_text', 'From the initial contact to the close out of a project, our customers can be assured that we are fully engaged in executing their vision. With direction from our solid Project Management Team we are able to manage all aspects of the mechanical installation in a professional and timely manner.\r\n\r\nOur Formula for Success:\r\n<strong>LAN &gt; MATERIAL &gt; MANPOWER</strong>'),
