(4138, 314, 'section_4_content_1_text', 'World Class Contracting takes great pride in being a part of the design of a project. Including us in the design process helps to eliminate many design conflicts that can occur structurally, architecturally and between the other trades. This proactive approach in turn helps to save the project time and money early on.'),
(4139, 314, '_section_4_content_1_text', 'field_5c48efe172bf1'),
(4140, 314, 'section_4_content_2_image', '307'),
(4141, 314, '_section_4_content_2_image', 'field_5c48f4fdd276b'),
(4142, 314, 'section_4_content_2_headline', 'IPD'),
(4143, 314, '_section_4_content_2_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(4144, 314, 'section_4_content_2_text', 'World Class Contracting has become well versed in the relatively new IPD philosophy and process. Similar to a Design Build approach; working as a team from the beginning of the IPD project creates a well thought out plan of what the owner envisions, and has proven to be a very effective way to deliver an exceptional final project.'),
(4145, 314, '_section_4_content_2_text', 'field_5c48efe172bf1'),
(4146, 314, 'section_4_content_3_image', '308'),
