(4149, 314, '_section_4_content_3_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(4150, 314, 'section_4_content_3_text', 'We have the capability to provide and design 3D drawings which assist in visual planning and enables prefabrication welding for mechanical rooms, which is an advantage to construction schedules.We also have our own Fab Shop centrally located to bring these designs to life.'),
