(6447, 366, '_section_4_content_2_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(6448, 366, 'section_4_content_2_text', 'World Class Contracting has become well versed in the relatively new IPD philosophy and process. Similar to a Design Build approach; working as a team from the beginning of the IPD project creates a well thought out plan of what the owner envisions, and has proven to be a very effective way to deliver an exceptional final project.'),
