(1300, 157, 'section_4_text', 'WCC continues to innovate, by being open to new ideas, offering a flexible approach and an eagerness to work with our clients as partners to devise the most cost-effective and practical solutions in developing Mechanical Systems. We encourage collaboration and welcomes new challenges and opportunities. Our Customers can rely on our design and construction team to produce extraordinary results, on time and on budget.\r\n\r\nWe are Members of various organizations RDCA, MCA, Lean Institute, AceBim, and IPD. Our team has been recognized in our industry by our peers for numerous Awards & Accomplishments including RDCA Subcontractor of the Year, Top Apprentice recognition, Scholarships, Grants and World Skills awards. Together we have created a World Class team of friends, families, and co-workers that genuinely care about one another as we continue to collaborate taking pride in our work and in striving to be the best.\r\n\r\n2017 Winner of the RDCA Sub-Contractor of the Year Award \r\n2015 Winner of the RDCA Sub-Contractor of the Year Award\r\n'),
