(1484, 16, 'section_4_content_1_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd assures that the safety of its employees, the employees of others on the job site, and the general public at large, is given the highest priority in all aspects of the firm’s activities. World Class Contracting Ltd will strive to provide its employees with the proper training and education required to enable the company to meet the stated goals of a safe workplace.'),
