(2679, 231, '_section_4_content_0_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(2680, 231, 'section_4_content_0_text', 'The World Class Contracting Estimating Team has extensive knowledge and experience in the industry and works diligently to provide the most up to date, fair and honest quotes for our customers pre-designed projects. Offering cost saving where available and insight into ways to get the most out of their pre-designed projects. We have well established relationships with our subtrades, offering  our customers an impressive, well rounded Mechanical team.'),
(2681, 231, '_section_4_content_0_text', 'field_5c48efe172bf1'),
(2682, 231, 'section_4_content_1_headline', 'Design Build'),
(2683, 231, '_section_4_content_1_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(2684, 231, 'section_4_content_1_text', 'World Class Contracting takes great pride in being a part of the design of a project. Including us in the design process helps to eliminate many design conflicts that can occur structurally, architecturally and between the other trades. This proactive approach in turn helps to save the project time and money early on.\r\n'),
(2685, 231, '_section_4_content_1_text', 'field_5c48efe172bf1'),
(2686, 231, 'section_4_content_2_headline', 'IPD'),
(2687, 231, '_section_4_content_2_headline', 'field_5c48efda72bf0'),
(2688, 231, 'section_4_content_2_text', 'World Class Contracting has become well versed in the relatively new IPD philosophy and process. Similar to a Design Build approach; working as a team from the beginning of the IPD project creates a well thought out plan of what the owner envisions, and has proven to be a very effective way to deliver an exceptional final project.'),
(2689, 231, '_section_4_content_2_text', 'field_5c48efe172bf1'),
