(2834, 236, 'section_3_content_0_headline', 'Our History'),
(2835, 236, '_section_3_content_0_headline', 'field_5c4a484e4bbe7'),
(2836, 236, 'section_3_content_0_text', 'The corporation was founded in 1999 out of Dickson Alberta, and then moved on to establish operation headquarters out of Red Deer Alberta in 2005. The company has continued to grow to become one of the most prominent Mechanical Contractors in Central Alberta.'),
(2837, 236, '_section_3_content_0_text', 'field_5c4a48554bbe8'),
(2838, 236, 'section_3_content_0_image', '104'),
(2839, 236, '_section_3_content_0_image', 'field_5c4a481d4bbe6'),
(2840, 236, 'section_3_content_1_headline', 'Commitment to Our Work'),
(2841, 236, '_section_3_content_1_headline', 'field_5c4a484e4bbe7'),
(2842, 236, 'section_3_content_1_text', 'From the initial contact to the close out of a project, our customers can be assured that we are fully engaged in executing their vision. With direction from our solid Project Management Team we are able to manage all aspects of the mechanical installation in a professional and timely manner. \r\n\r\nOur Formula for Success:  PLAN > MATERIAL > MANPOWER\r\n'),
(2843, 236, '_section_3_content_1_text', 'field_5c4a48554bbe8'),
(2844, 236, 'section_3_content_1_image', '104'),
(2845, 236, '_section_3_content_1_image', 'field_5c4a481d4bbe6'),
(2846, 236, 'section_3_content', '2'),
(2847, 236, '_section_3_content', 'field_5c4a480b4bbe5'),
(2848, 236, 'section_4_headline', 'We are recognized by our clients and peers for our customer service, commitment to safety, and quality workmanship.'),
(2849, 236, '_section_4_headline', 'field_5c4a48694bbe9'),
(2850, 236, 'section_4_text', 'WCC continues to innovate, by being open to new ideas, offering a flexible approach and an eagerness to work with our clients as partners to devise the most cost-effective and practical solutions in developing Mechanical Systems. We encourage collaboration and welcomes new challenges and opportunities. Our Customers can rely on our design and construction team to produce extraordinary results, on time and on budget.\r\n\r\nWe are Members of various organizations RDCA, MCA, Lean Institute, AceBim, and IPD. Our team has been recognized in our industry by our peers for numerous Awards & Accomplishments including RDCA Subcontractor of the Year, Top Apprentice recognition, Scholarships, Grants and World Skills awards. Together we have created a World Class team of friends, families, and co-workers that genuinely care about one another as we continue to collaborate taking pride in our work and in striving to be the best.\r\n\r\n2017 Winner of the RDCA Sub-Contractor of the Year Award \r\n2015 Winner of the RDCA Sub-Contractor of the Year Award\r\n'),
