(3719, 244, '_section_2_headline', 'field_5c4b46ff25f41'),
(3720, 244, 'section_2_text', 'The World Class Contracting Mission is to live up to our company name on every project from start to finish. Our goal is to continue our success as a proven leader in the Mechanical Construction Industry, providing our customers with the best value in their Construction projects.\r\nWe train and retain professional people with a strong work ethic, who take pride in their work. Our team continues to build upon our reputation, recognized as a world-class organization with the highest levels of safety, craftsmanship, and integrity\r\n'),
