(3735, 244, '_cta_button_link_right', 'field_page_5bfef79b9536c'),
(3736, 244, 'section_4_content_0_headline', 'Honesty and Integrity'),
(3737, 244, '_section_4_content_0_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(3738, 244, 'section_4_content_0_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. serves its customers and treats its competitors, subcontractors and suppliers with honesty and integrity. We avoid conflicts of interest, both corporate and individual. Where a corporate conflict exists, World Class Contracting Ltd will disclose such conflict to its customer or prospective customer. World Class Contracting Ltd. regularly educates its staff about personal conflicts of interest and has established a procedure for internal disclosure. World Class Contracting Ltd. does not knowingly violate any law or regulation'),
(3739, 244, '_section_4_content_0_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(3740, 244, 'section_4_content_0_image', '172'),
(3741, 244, '_section_4_content_0_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(3742, 244, 'section_4_content_1_headline', 'Safety'),
(3743, 244, '_section_4_content_1_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(3744, 244, 'section_4_content_1_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd assures that the safety of its employees, the employees of others on the job site, and the general public at large, is given the highest priority in all aspects of the firm’s activities. World Class Contracting Ltd will strive to provide its employees with the proper training and education required to enable the company to meet the stated goals of a safe workplace.'),
(3745, 244, '_section_4_content_1_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(3746, 244, 'section_4_content_1_image', '172'),
(3747, 244, '_section_4_content_1_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(3748, 244, 'section_4_content_2_headline', 'Environmental Accountability'),
(3749, 244, '_section_4_content_2_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(3750, 244, 'section_4_content_2_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. will endeavour to promote sustainable building practices and environmental considerations in all its operations and in the services it provides to its clients.  World Class Contracting Ltd will strive to provide its employees with the proper training and education required to enable the company to meet the stated goals of a more sustainable built environment and more environmentally friendly business practices.\r\n'),
(3751, 244, '_section_4_content_2_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(3752, 244, 'section_4_content_2_image', '172'),
(3753, 244, '_section_4_content_2_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(3754, 244, 'section_4_content_3_headline', 'Standards of Practice '),
(3755, 244, '_section_4_content_3_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(3756, 244, 'section_4_content_3_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. provides materials and services in a manner consistent with the established and accepted standards of the construction industry and with the laws and regulations that govern it including the use of standard industry documents wherever feasible. The firm performs its contracts with competence, reasonable care and diligence. The firm establishes prices that are commensurate with its services.\r\n'),
(3757, 244, '_section_4_content_3_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(3758, 244, 'section_4_content_3_image', '172'),
(3759, 244, '_section_4_content_3_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(3760, 244, 'section_4_content_4_headline', 'Competition'),
(3761, 244, '_section_4_content_4_headline', 'field_5c4b4b6babd4c'),
(3762, 244, 'section_4_content_4_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. competes fairly for contracts, avoiding any practice that might be construed to be in violation of the letter or spirit of federal or provincial competition or unfair business practices legislation. The firm does not seek nor accept information concerning a competitor’s bid prior to bid closing nor does it attempt to modify its price after the bid closing. The firm avoids any activity that could be construed as *bid shopping, a **reverse bid auction or ***bid peddling.\r\n'),
(3763, 244, '_section_4_content_4_text', 'field_5c4b4b73abd4d'),
(3764, 244, 'section_4_content_4_image', '172'),
(3765, 244, '_section_4_content_4_image', 'field_5c4b4b7cabd4e'),
(3766, 244, 'section_4_content', '5'),
(3767, 244, '_section_4_content', 'field_5c4b473525f44'),
(3768, 244, 'section_5_content_0_headline', 'Health & Safety'),
(3769, 244, '_section_5_content_0_headline', 'field_5c4b4b94abd50'),
(3770, 244, 'section_5_content_0_text', 'World Class Contracting Ltd. is committed to working with our employees in order to create working conditions that promote safe, healthy, and efficient operations and to eliminate or control hazards that cause incidents, injuries or damage to the environment. We believe excellence in practice is vital to the wellbeing of all people directly or indirectly involved in our business.\r\n<strong>We maintain a Certificate of Recognition (COR) for our Safety Program.\r\n</strong>\r\n'),
(3771, 244, '_section_5_content_0_text', 'field_5c4b4b9aabd51'),
(3772, 244, 'section_5_content_0_icon', '170'),
(3773, 244, '_section_5_content_0_icon', 'field_5c4b4ba4abd52'),
(3774, 244, 'section_5_content_1_headline', 'What is COR?'),
(3775, 244, '_section_5_content_1_headline', 'field_5c4b4b94abd50'),
(3776, 244, 'section_5_content_1_text', 'A COR shows that the employer’s health and safety management system has been evaluated by a certified auditor and meets provincial standards. These standards are established by Occupational Health and Safety (OHS). It aims to reduce the human and financial costs associated with workplace accidents and injuries. The COR certification is the highest distinction available in the industry.\r\n'),
(3777, 244, '_section_5_content_1_text', 'field_5c4b4b9aabd51'),
(3778, 244, 'section_5_content_1_icon', '170'),
(3779, 244, '_section_5_content_1_icon', 'field_5c4b4ba4abd52'),
(3780, 244, 'section_5_content_2_headline', 'Our Commitment to Health & Safety'),
(3781, 244, '_section_5_content_2_headline', 'field_5c4b4b94abd50'),
(3782, 244, 'section_5_content_2_text', 'The Management at World Class Contracting Ltd., is committed to maintaining a safe and healthy workplace while protecting the environment. We continuously strive to improve our HSE Performance and prevent injuries and illness by maintaining stringent policies and procedures, meeting or exceeding all applicable laws and regulations.\r\n'),
